00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:38,250
Jangan khawatir.

239
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:41,520
Namun, kami baru kembali,
mereka sudah mengejar.

240
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,530
Katanya ini pertandingan akademi,
