281
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:25,320
Oh iya.

282
00:16:25,350 --> 00:16:26,590
Yu Tianheng sangat hebat.

283
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:27,890
Aku sudah mengalahkannya.

284
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:28,520
Sungguh?

285
